    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Is everyone just fending for themselves - or is there any empathy left after all?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Facing the rain&quot; is a story-driven RPG, without battles but with impactful decisions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the role of Billy, a young girl embarking on her first job as a hotel maid, in a town called Drumberg - which is nowhere in particular. Soon she realizes, there is a tragic heaviness weighing down on the hotel and its people. But she has the power to transform the place - if she makes the right choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294370/extras/db75e5b8fd3225225a2d29f4428c0a91.poster.avif?t=1765838656\" width=307 height=61 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294370/extras/db75e5b8fd3225225a2d29f4428c0a91.webm?t=1765838656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game interactively tells a fictional yet relatable story centered around themes of grief and depression, but also positivity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player’s actions will determine the outcome of the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide your character through an immersive 2D pixel-graphics-based world. Make your way to the hotel, discover the building and its surroundings, go into town and visit shops, and explore a metaphorical forest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with other characters: The player will meet different types of characters that present opinions or problems that require to engage thoughtfully.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the main plot, you will collect items and solve problems or puzzles in an adventure-style manner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secrets and succeed in challenges to unlock steam achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomized elements add variety to each playthrough, enhancing the game’s replay value.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains original music crafted exclusively for the story that is being told.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playtime is roughly 2-3 hours. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294370/extras/0973cf2829901f67945a3f2188494f13.avif?t=1765838656\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294370/extras_big/0973cf2829901f67945a3f2188494f13.avif?t=1765838656 width=800 height=49 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Controls:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard: WASD or Cursor buttons (configurable)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller supported (Xbox, Dualshock via USB)<br><i>We recommend launching the game with &quot;Disable Steam Input&quot; option under Properties -&gt; Controller</i></p></li></ul>",
